# 🎮 GameTimeConverter - Game Time Converter Tool (English)

## 📌 Introduction
GameTimeConverter is a **Windows application** that converts **game time (EGT, UTC-2) into Taipei Time (TST, UTC+8) and New York Time (EST/EDT, UTC-5/UTC-4).**

🔹 **Key Features**
- 🎮 **Game Time Conversion**: Converts **EGT (UTC-2)** into **TST (UTC+8)** and **New York Time**.
- ⏳ **Easy Input**: Enter time using **`yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm`** format.

---

## 📥 Download
🔗 [📎 Click here to download the latest release](https://github.com/bghosth/GameTimeConverter/releases)

---

## 🔄 Future Updates
✅ More time zone support  
✅ **Automatic Daylight Saving Time (DST) adjustment**  
✅ Date Picker for easier input  
✅ Multi-language support  

---

## 💻 System Requirements
- 🖥️ **OS**: Windows 7 / 8 / 10 / 11
- 📦 **.NET Framework**: 4.7.2 or later
- 💾 **Disk Space**: Less than 10MB

---

## 🛠️ How to Use
1️⃣ **Download and run `GameTimeConverter.exe`**  
2️⃣ **Enter game time** (format `yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm`)  
3️⃣ **Press `Enter` or click the convert button**  
4️⃣ **Check the converted Taipei and New York time results**  

